# Spec-first, brief responses

**Atlas:** `docs/specs/system/token-hover.atlas.supplement.md` — token hover / trace / dim / pending.

## When explaining behavior

- Link the atlas + owning spec; do **not** copy spec tables or mermaid into chat.
- ≤6 bullets or one small table unless the user asks for depth.
- Code citations only for the line under discussion.

